      <title>南非的拉马福萨（Ramaphosa）寻求与种族隔离受害者的定居点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-seeks-settlement-with-apartheid-victims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨（Cyril Ramaphosa）的法律团队将开始进行谈判，以解决种族隔离时代犯罪受害者的家庭对他和几个政府机构提起的诉讼，他们说该州阻碍了他们寻求正义的企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-seeks-settlement-with-apartheid-victims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 11:12:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国绿党目前拒绝梅尔斯的国防支出计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/germany-s-greens-won-t-support-draft-debt-package-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的绿党拒绝了一项债务资助的一揽子计划，该计划将在国防和基础设施支出中释放数十亿欧元，可能会使弗里德里希·梅尔兹（Friedrich Merz）的招待会征服弗里德里希·梅尔兹（Friedrich Merz），而无需通过这项立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/germany-s-greens-won-t-support-draft-debt-package-in-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 11:10:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
